---
const { image } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="about-me">
  <div class="top-section">
    <div class="intro-content">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        Hello! I'm <strong>Satya Raj Awasthi</strong>, a final-year Software Engineering undergraduate at <a href="https://ncit.edu.np/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>NCIT</strong></a>, <a href="https://pu.edu.np/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Pokhara University</strong></a>. I'm deeply fascinated by how software systems are designed, built, and evolved â€” and I enjoy exploring new ways to make them more efficient, reliable, and intelligent.
      </p>
      <p>
        I love studying and experimenting with software engineering principles, programming systems, databases, and distributed architectures, constantly trying to bridge theory and practice through exploration and experimentation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src={image} alt="Satya Raj Awasthi" class="profile-image" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p>
      Alongside my studies, I work as a Software Engineer at <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/esewa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>eSewa Ltd.</strong></a>, where I've gained hands-on experience building real-world systems at scale. I also lead and contribute to student technical communities, including serving as a <a href="https://githubcampus.expert/SatyaRajAwasth1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>GitHub Campus Expert</strong></a>, where I mentor peers and promote collaboration in open-source and technology education.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm currently seeking research or graduate (PhD) opportunities where I can explore challenging problems related to my research interests and grow as a researcher through active collaboration and experimentation.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-me {
    max-width: var(--content-width, 1000px);
    margin: 3rem auto 4rem;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .top-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .intro-content {
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .full-width-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  p a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  p a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .image-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 350px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .top-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .intro-content {
      padding-right: 0;
    }

    .image-container {
      position: static;
    }

    .profile-image {
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .full-width-content {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>